food_name: Sushi Platter
description: A delightful assortment of fresh nigiri and maki sushi, including tuna, salmon, shrimp, and avocado rolls. Served with pickled ginger, wasabi, and soy sauce.

food_name: Chicken Tikka Masala
description: Tender pieces of marinated chicken cooked in a rich tomato-based sauce with a blend of aromatic Indian spices. Served with fragrant basmati rice and warm naan bread.

food_name: Grilled Caesar Salad
description: Crisp romaine lettuce lightly grilled and tossed in creamy Caesar dressing, topped with garlic croutons, shaved Parmesan cheese, and grilled chicken breast.

food_name: Beef Bulgogi
description: Thinly sliced beef marinated in a sweet and savory blend of soy sauce, garlic, sesame oil, and spices, then grilled to perfection. Served with steamed rice and kimchi.

food_name: Caprese Salad
description: Fresh ripe tomatoes, creamy mozzarella cheese, and fragrant basil leaves drizzled with extra virgin olive oil and balsamic glaze. A simple yet delicious Italian classic.

food_name: Pho
description: A fragrant beef broth simmered with spices, rice noodles, and tender slices of beef, garnished with fresh herbs, bean sprouts, lime wedges, and chili peppers.

food_name: Margherita Pizza
description: Thin-crust pizza topped with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, basil leaves, and a drizzle of olive oil. A classic Neapolitan pizza that's simple yet bursting with flavor.

food_name: Chocolate Lava Cake
description: A decadent chocolate cake with a molten chocolate center, served warm with a scoop of vanilla ice cream. A heavenly dessert that melts in your mouth.
